WEBVTT

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:48.700
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.420 --> 00:00:51.780
=Episode 6=

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:01.679
Who are you?

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.520
You should be telling me that.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:06.280
Who exactly are you?

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:08.479
Save it.

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:09.840
You can't tough it out.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:11.719
This is sodium thiopental,

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.430
commonly known as the truth serum.

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.159
Spill it.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:16.760
Ye Chen.

00:01:18.319 --> 00:01:19.159
Orphan.

00:01:20.319 --> 00:01:22.280
The son-in-law of the Xiao family.

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:23.159
What did Tang Sihai

00:01:23.439 --> 00:01:24.719
send you to do?

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:27.990
Did he send you to find
the medicine formula in Xiao family?

00:01:28.519 --> 00:01:29.560
What medicine formula?

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:31.400
I don't know.

00:01:32.359 --> 00:01:33.680
Think about your wife.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.519
If you don't want her to be in danger,

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:40.159
just spill it.

00:02:18.039 --> 00:02:18.719
Let's go!

00:02:33.159 --> 00:02:33.520
Mr. Ye.

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:35.039
Mr. Ye?

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:44.639
Who are they?

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:46.759
Why didn't you tell me...

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:49.360
that an heir has to go through this?

00:02:51.479 --> 00:02:52.919
If you want to be the heir,

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:55.360
you have to take on the risks.

00:02:56.400 --> 00:02:58.159
Are you hiding something from me?

00:02:59.759 --> 00:03:01.599
They kept talking
about a medicine formula.

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:07.879
Mr. Ye.

00:03:08.919 --> 00:03:10.039
You have

00:03:10.039 --> 00:03:12.400
congenital stellate ganglion
hyperactivity syndrome,

00:03:12.610 --> 00:03:14.560
which gives you
extraordinary cognitive abilities

00:03:14.719 --> 00:03:16.000
and an exceptional memory.

00:03:16.639 --> 00:03:18.479
But that made your brain's oxygen demand

00:03:18.479 --> 00:03:20.390
exceed what your heart and lungs
could compensate for.

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:21.520
This led

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:22.319
to brain atrophy

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:24.080
and multi-organ failure symptoms.

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:26.159
Your parents developed a new medicine

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:27.479
to save you,

00:03:27.670 --> 00:03:29.560
which successfully
controlled your condition.

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.520
You should remember
quite a few things now.

00:03:33.199 --> 00:03:35.000
Do you remember what you learned

00:03:35.479 --> 00:03:36.520
from Mr. Quan

00:03:36.719 --> 00:03:37.919
when you were little?

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:41.360
Astronomy, geography,

00:03:42.080 --> 00:03:43.280
astrology,

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.680
medicine, antique appraisal,

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:47.680
and martial arts.

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:49.960
If it weren't for your condition,

00:03:50.879 --> 00:03:52.319
you couldn't have learned so quickly

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:54.039
or learned so much.

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:55.800
Then one day,

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.320
your condition flared up again.

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.400
It was Mr. Quan

00:03:58.759 --> 00:04:00.960
who saved you using his lifelong skills.

00:04:01.479 --> 00:04:02.159
But

00:04:03.039 --> 00:04:04.400
you forgot

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:05.680
most of what you learned.

00:04:07.639 --> 00:04:09.520
So what about the medicine?

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:10.800
The medicine

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:12.800
didn't just control your condition.

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:14.680
It also has a unique effect

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:15.840
on certain cancers.

00:04:16.039 --> 00:04:18.479
That's why your parents
decided to return immediately

00:04:18.919 --> 00:04:21.080
and make the formula available for free.

00:04:21.800 --> 00:04:22.519
Unfortunately,

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:24.600
they died

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:25.920
in that car accident.

00:04:26.959 --> 00:04:27.800
The medicine formula

00:04:28.360 --> 00:04:29.279
also went missing.

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:33.160
After years of investigation,

00:04:33.519 --> 00:04:35.480
we found out
that the formula last appeared

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:36.920
in Old Mr. Xiao's hands.

00:04:38.759 --> 00:04:39.399
So, Mr. Ye,

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:42.360
you must help us find that formula.

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:45.240
You had this all planned out,
didn't you?

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:46.079
That's right.

00:04:47.010 --> 00:04:48.319
You've been plotting against me?

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:49.600
You dragged me into this?

00:04:50.199 --> 00:04:50.639
Yes.

00:04:51.319 --> 00:04:52.480
You think I'm a pawn?

00:04:52.630 --> 00:04:53.399
Find it yourself.

00:04:54.879 --> 00:04:55.639
Calculate how much

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:57.279
of our money he's spent.

00:04:57.439 --> 00:04:59.920
I remember that jade necklace
cost us millions.

00:05:00.279 --> 00:05:01.439
Pay it back within a month.

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:02.240
Charge him

00:05:02.399 --> 00:05:04.279
a daily late fee of 0.1%.

00:05:04.519 --> 00:05:05.759
If he can't pay up, sue him

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:06.879
for credit card fraud.

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:07.720
Also...

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:08.519
I...

00:05:09.959 --> 00:05:12.000
Tear up the contract with Xiao Group.

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:13.000
Tell them

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.000
that Dihao Group

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:16.160
will no longer work with Xiao Churan.

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:17.079
Noted.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:18.639
That's too much.

00:05:19.519 --> 00:05:20.000
Punk,

00:05:20.879 --> 00:05:22.319
listen up.

00:05:23.319 --> 00:05:26.519
I can lift up your precious Xiao Churan,

00:05:27.079 --> 00:05:28.759
or I can bring her down.

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:29.720
You...

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.439
You're so annoying.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.839
I was just joking with you.

00:05:41.439 --> 00:05:42.120
Seriously.

00:05:42.439 --> 00:05:43.800
It's just a medicine formula.

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:46.040
Go find it, then.

00:05:46.639 --> 00:05:47.079
On it.

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:10.959
Mom,

00:06:11.439 --> 00:06:12.560
enough already.

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:13.830
You've been laughing all night.

00:06:14.079 --> 00:06:15.879
This is too funny.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.720
It's been so many years since our family

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.959
has had such a win.

00:06:22.879 --> 00:06:23.519
Welcome back.

00:06:24.079 --> 00:06:24.680
Mom, Dad.

00:06:25.279 --> 00:06:27.000
Why were you gone so long?

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:29.279
Tang just got dumped recently.

00:06:29.480 --> 00:06:30.360
He's really upset.

00:06:30.360 --> 00:06:31.319
I stayed to talk with him.

00:06:31.319 --> 00:06:32.040
Is he okay?

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:33.759
Yeah, he's fine.

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:37.480
Isn't he deaf, though?

00:06:38.759 --> 00:06:39.360
Body language.

00:06:39.770 --> 00:06:40.360
Body language.

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:42.680
Chen.

00:06:43.879 --> 00:06:45.199
I have something to tell you.

00:06:47.319 --> 00:06:47.680
Mom,

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:48.879
what do you need?

00:06:48.879 --> 00:06:50.439
I need to remind you of something.

00:06:50.879 --> 00:06:52.639
The most important thing
for you right now

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:54.560
is to take good care of Wang Dongxue.

00:06:55.279 --> 00:06:57.439
She's our biggest support.

00:06:57.680 --> 00:06:58.759
Don't worry.

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.480
I'm really good
at taking care of people. Right?

00:07:03.319 --> 00:07:04.560
Here, let me pour you a drink.

00:07:05.060 --> 00:07:05.720
- Mom.
- Here.

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:06.079
Okay.

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:06.720
Thanks.

00:07:07.279 --> 00:07:08.959
Tonight, just drink heartily.

00:07:08.959 --> 00:07:09.720
Alright.

00:07:10.120 --> 00:07:10.600
I'll drink.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:11.360
You guys eat.

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:12.500
I'm going out for some fresh air.

00:07:12.519 --> 00:07:13.000
What?

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:15.400
Go after her.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:18.720
Churan,

00:07:19.279 --> 00:07:19.920
what's wrong?

00:07:20.199 --> 00:07:21.319
Are you feeling sick?

00:07:22.500 --> 00:07:23.680
Is it because I didn't toast you?

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.600
Or is it because our agreement
is ending?

00:07:25.600 --> 00:07:26.720
Is that why you're upset?

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:28.319
It's okay. I can always renew it.

00:07:29.480 --> 00:07:30.360
What's wrong with you?

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:31.240
Say something.

00:07:32.550 --> 00:07:34.680
Are you scared of Xiao Hailong
doing something shady?

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.680
Or are you feeling the pressure

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:37.690
of being the chairperson?

00:07:37.720 --> 00:07:38.160
It's fine.

00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:38.720
I'm here.

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:40.480
We've already latched onto Wang Dongxue.

00:07:44.839 --> 00:07:46.000
You're jealous, huh?

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:49.399
Churan, wait.

00:07:50.120 --> 00:07:51.040
Who else would

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:52.600
have feelings for me except for you?

00:07:52.720 --> 00:07:53.319
Besides,

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:54.279
I only know Wang Dongxue

00:07:54.279 --> 00:07:55.560
because of Tang.

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:57.160
It's not what you think.

00:07:58.240 --> 00:07:59.240
What are you thinking?

00:08:00.199 --> 00:08:00.920
Finally talking.

00:08:01.639 --> 00:08:02.560
You're finally talking.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:04.079
Can you be serious for once?

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:06.519
I'm serious.

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:08.199
I'm really serious now.

00:08:09.439 --> 00:08:10.079
Ye Chen,

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:13.040
I really appreciate everything
you've done for me.

00:08:13.199 --> 00:08:15.279
I'm really happy I get the chance

00:08:15.279 --> 00:08:16.720
to run Grandpa's company.

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:17.800
You...

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:20.720
You're my wife.

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.630
I'm glad you're happy.

00:08:22.959 --> 00:08:25.519
But I don't want you
bending over so much.

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:29.000
I don't want you always
trying to please Wang Dongxue.

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:31.480
I don't want you to owe her
such a big favor for me.

00:08:35.240 --> 00:08:36.000
All these years,

00:08:36.439 --> 00:08:38.159
I've been polite with everyone.

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:38.960
I'm used to it.

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:43.000
Okay.

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.759
I'll buy a back support belt tomorrow,

00:08:44.759 --> 00:08:45.960
so I can stand up straight.

00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:46.960
Look.

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:48.039
Like this.

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:49.000
Okay?

00:08:50.799 --> 00:08:51.679
I,

00:08:52.039 --> 00:08:52.840
Ye Chen,

00:08:53.120 --> 00:08:54.759
am a chairperson's husband

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:57.000
and the best son-in-law in Jinzhou.

00:08:57.720 --> 00:08:58.440
I

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:00.639
am the peerless son-in-law.

00:09:05.879 --> 00:09:06.840
Smug.

00:09:09.500 --> 00:09:10.480
Who are you calling smug?

00:09:10.879 --> 00:09:11.519
Churan.

00:09:18.610 --> 00:09:19.600
Dad, what are you doing?

00:09:20.799 --> 00:09:21.919
You bought a fake again?

00:09:22.559 --> 00:09:23.600
You scared me to death.

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:24.639
What are you yelling for?

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:26.120
If you woke your mom up,

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:28.399
it's another war between us.

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:29.960
Seriously.

00:09:33.559 --> 00:09:34.120
Look at this.

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:37.080
This time, it's a bargain.

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:38.639
This is a Yuan Dynasty porcelain.

00:09:38.639 --> 00:09:39.559
Yuan Dynasty.

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:40.679
The kiln's too hot.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:41.960
The flame's too intense.

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:43.960
It's been soaked in aging solution.

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:45.039
Nonsense.

00:09:45.399 --> 00:09:46.600
This one's deep.

00:09:48.610 --> 00:09:50.679
Yuan Dynasty official kilns
never used reign marks.

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:53.080
(Zhengda Year One)
Jingdezhen's clay?

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:54.840
Dad,

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:56.559
it's not a bargain.

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.720
Calling it a fake is being generous.

00:09:59.919 --> 00:10:01.720
You know antiques too?

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:04.279
I learned a little.

00:10:04.759 --> 00:10:05.559
Actually,

00:10:06.279 --> 00:10:07.039
I know

00:10:07.639 --> 00:10:08.720
the stuff I buy

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:10.440
is never real.

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:12.120
I learned it all from my dad.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:14.039
It's just

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:15.120
an impulse buy.

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:18.000
Do you know Old Mr. Xiao well?

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:18.960
Of course.

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:20.879
He's my dad. Of course, I know him.

00:10:21.559 --> 00:10:21.919
Well,

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:23.200
did he ever

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:24.759
collect things?

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:26.080
Like old books, ancient paintings,

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:27.039
antiques, and formulas.

00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:28.360
Medicine ones.

00:10:29.639 --> 00:10:31.600
They say these are worth a lot now.

00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:33.320
Medicine formulas?

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:34.360
Never heard of it.

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:35.850
He had copper coins.

00:10:38.559 --> 00:10:39.360
I'll leave you to it.

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:43.159
Don't tell your mom, okay?

00:10:43.159 --> 00:10:43.679
Got it.

00:10:48.840 --> 00:10:49.759
Missing your grandpa?

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:53.000
I dreamed about him last night.

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:54.120
Look at this photo.

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:57.879
This was when I was six.

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:00.360
He bought me my first camera.

00:11:00.360 --> 00:11:01.840
I took my first photo with it.

00:11:03.570 --> 00:11:04.559
That's pretty meaningful.

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:06.440
This vase looks nice.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:07.840
Grandpa called it

00:11:08.080 --> 00:11:08.799
the medicine jar.

00:11:09.840 --> 00:11:12.039
He said a friend of his gave it to him.

00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:13.279
It could save a lot of people.

00:11:16.039 --> 00:11:18.039
We found out
that the formula last appeared

00:11:18.039 --> 00:11:19.399
in Old Mr. Xiao's hands.

00:11:26.039 --> 00:11:28.879
(So my dad gave the formula
to the Xiao family.)

00:11:30.679 --> 00:11:31.240
Ye Chen.

00:11:32.159 --> 00:11:32.679
Ye Chen?

00:11:34.120 --> 00:11:35.390
Where's this medicine jar now?

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:38.320
Grandpa put it away before he passed.

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:40.879
It should be in the safe
where he kept his stuff.

00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:45.720
Seems like I've found it.

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:46.200
What?

00:11:46.759 --> 00:11:47.440
Nothing.

00:11:48.620 --> 00:11:49.519
Where's the safe now?

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:53.240
It's in Grandpa's study in the basement.

00:11:53.240 --> 00:11:55.399
After he passed,
that room got locked up.

00:11:55.570 --> 00:11:56.200
Where's the key?

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:57.759
Grandma has it.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:00.440
But anyone who becomes the chairperson

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:01.759
will get the key.

00:12:04.559 --> 00:12:07.000
(So as long as I get the key,
I can wrap this up.)

00:12:10.279 --> 00:12:11.440
Grandma,

00:12:11.440 --> 00:12:13.159
say something.

00:12:13.840 --> 00:12:16.480
Are you really letting Xiao Churan
be the chairperson?

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:17.399
Not happy about it?

00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:19.799
Well, fight for it, then.

00:12:20.039 --> 00:12:20.440
I...

00:12:22.600 --> 00:12:24.320
I've been fighting for it.

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:26.679
I've got a plan for you.

00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:32.440
Remember Dong Ruolin,
Churan's college friend?

00:12:33.320 --> 00:12:34.000
By the way,

00:12:34.350 --> 00:12:36.360
Dong Ruolin said
she's coming to work in Jinzhou.

00:12:36.639 --> 00:12:38.080
She'll be here tomorrow afternoon.

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:38.790
I'll pick her up.

00:12:40.399 --> 00:12:42.679
You mean the one
whom Xiao Hailong used to pursue?

00:12:43.440 --> 00:12:43.960
Yeah.

00:12:44.399 --> 00:12:46.000
Her family is also

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:47.799
one of the prominent families
in Yanjing.

00:12:48.519 --> 00:12:50.279
If you can win her over,

00:12:50.559 --> 00:12:51.200
maybe

00:12:51.519 --> 00:12:54.159
you can compete with Xiao Churan
for the chairperson spot.

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:55.679
Let's do this.

00:12:56.200 --> 00:12:57.720
When you're done with work tomorrow,

00:12:57.900 --> 00:12:59.039
we can pick her up together.

00:12:59.799 --> 00:13:01.600
Grandma,

00:13:02.279 --> 00:13:04.559
but my car's too old.

00:13:04.559 --> 00:13:05.240
Old?

00:13:05.700 --> 00:13:07.080
Didn't you just buy it last year?

00:13:07.360 --> 00:13:09.039
Only a new one can make me look good.

00:13:09.039 --> 00:13:11.200
Only then can we show off our power

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:14.799
and my sincerity, Grandma.

00:13:16.759 --> 00:13:17.679
Grandma.

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:22.120
I really owe you.

00:13:22.120 --> 00:13:23.039
Thank you, Grandma.

00:13:23.759 --> 00:13:24.960
Time to buy a car.

00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:31.919
(I'm still the one calling the shots
in the Xiao family.)

00:13:51.982 --> 00:13:54.470
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:13:54.557 --> 00:13:58.310
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:13:58.770 --> 00:14:03.707
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:14:03.870 --> 00:14:06.157
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:14:06.470 --> 00:14:09.150
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:14:10.220 --> 00:14:12.845
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:14:13.145 --> 00:14:16.157
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:14:16.357 --> 00:14:19.407
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:14:19.520 --> 00:14:22.482
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:14:22.750 --> 00:14:25.907
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:14:26.132 --> 00:14:29.882
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:14:29.882 --> 00:14:32.745
♪I belong to no one♪

00:14:32.807 --> 00:14:36.257
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:14:36.257 --> 00:14:38.932
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:14:38.932 --> 00:14:45.270
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪